public class XYDataSinkSourceSeries extends AbstractXYSeriesDataSink
DataSink that appends data into series. A series is created for each individual data source.

Nick Collier

  • Constructor Details

    • XYDataSinkSourceSeries

      public XYDataSinkSourceSeries(BatchUpdateXYSeries xydata)
      Creates a XYDataSinkSourceSeries that will add series to the specified XYSeriesCollection and update those series. Each series records successive x and y values where the x value is the value of the "X" (e.g. tick) data source, and the y value is the value returned by that data source.
      Parameters:
      xydata -
